      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-chery-says-it-will-sign-deal-with-premium-european-auto-brand-over-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芜湖汽车制造商奇瑞 (CHERY.UL) 董事长尹同跃周日表示，该公司将与一家欧洲优质品牌签署平台合作协议。]]></description>
